         <abstract id="aspace_5200892865308e38c1e4a1866b7572ad">The collection consists of various documents collected by William Jay Foltz from the 1960s through the 1990s relating to political developments and conflicts in Senegal, Mali, Ghana, Chad, Nigeria, Uganda, Southern Rhodesia, Kenya and South Africa.</abstract>
    
